result.title: Need help to reach new heights
result.content:
Hello Codeforcers,

I would like to ask people who have experience in solving dfs problems and dp problems and anything related if they can suggest good resources for newbies such as myself to read and understand these types of algorithms and their take on these resources would be appreciated.

And i would like to add if they have any input on the way of studying and approaching these algorithms should be that would also be nice and i would be grateful.
